<h1 class="chapter-title">Chapter 11 – Tanhai</h1>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Tanhai koi khaali jagah nahi hoti,  
    balki woh jagah hoti hai jahan yaadein bolti hain.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Woh bheed mein bhi akela tha.  
    Log hans rahe the, baatein chal rahi thi,  
    par uske andar ek khamoshi thi jo shor se bhi tez thi.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Usne kai baar socha tha,  
    shayad waqt ke saath sab theek ho jayega.
    Par tanhai ne use sikhaya —
    kuch cheezein theek nahi hoti,  
    bas aadat ban jaati hain.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Raat ko jab sab so jaate,  
    tab uski tanhai jaag jaati.
    Har yaad, har baat,
    bina ijazat uske paas aa jaati.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Kabhi-kabhi woh khud se poochta —
    “Galti meri thi ya kismat ki?”
    Par jawaab kabhi mila hi nahi.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Tanhai ne use todha nahi,
    bas thoda chup kar diya.
    Ab woh kam bolta hai,
    par zyada mehsoos karta hai.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="page">
  <p>
    Shayad tanhai bhi zaroori hoti hai,
    taaki insaan apne aap se mil sake.
  </p>

  <a href="../index.html" class="big-btn">⬅️ Novel Home</a>

